Usage: create_ccopt_macro_model_spec [-help] [-ckSpec]
                                     [-ediCtsSpecForMacroModels <string>]
                                     [-file <string>]

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
-ckSpec                                # use Spec-based CCOpt CTS flow
                                       # (bool, optional)
-ediCtsSpecForMacroModels <string>     # specify EDI CTS spec for macro models
                                       # (string, optional)
-file <string>                         # export CCOpt macro model spec
                                       # (string, optional)